InfoPage3_Text1: Appear on reel 1,2,3,4,5, collect 3 or more symbols to enter bonus game
InfoPage3_Text2:
During bonus game, 3 magic globe will be rewarded corresponding to the bonus rewards on the magic globe.
There's a chance that the magic globe will fall on any empty spot with their corresponding bonuses.
Each spin consumes one energy bar, the game ends when three energy bars are cleared.
As long as you get 1 magic globe during any spin, the energy bar will be filled up.
When game ends, the total bonus on the magic globe will be awarded.

InfoPage3_Tip1:
The wild symbol can replace all symbols except SCATTERl;
the wild symbol will only appear on the 2nd, 3rd, 4th and 5th reels
Every time the wild symbol appears, it is randomly multiplied by X1,
X2 or X3.During payout, if there are one or more wild symbols on the
winning line,  the multiplier will be multiplied during payout

3 or more bonus symbols appearing on any reel,

When 3 or more bonus symbols appear,
get 5 times the bet reward

InfoPage4_Tip2:
The FREE SPINS round can be instantly
triggered from the base game by buying it
for 100x the current total bet. When buying the FREE SPINS
feature, 3,4, or 5 SCATTERS can hit randomly on the triggering screen and 8,12, or 16 freespins will be awarded.
